  "accessibility_and_testing": {
    "test_ids_required": true,
    "test_id_convention": "kebab-case, role-based (e.g., login-submit-button)",
    "contrast": "Ensure gold text on dark background meets 4.5:1 ratio"
  },
  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Use Expo React Native SDK 54. All styles must adhere to the provided color palette (Jewel & Luxury: Dark + Gold). Apply generic `data-testid` to all interactive elements for robust automated testing. Load `Playfair Display` for headings and `Manrope` for body via expo-font. Do NOT use Inter. Rely on borders instead of heavy shadows for elevation. The app contains dual logic (Admin/User), ensure navigation and state separation is managed correctly. Implement INR (₹) currency formatting for all payments and revenues. Build standard React Native styles mapping to this JSON guideline."
}